    "description": "O'will Corporation engages in the import/export and sale of food and drink materials in Japan and internationally. The company provides vitamin, calcium, amino acid, emulsifier, stabilizer, nutritional fortifier, dietary fiber, flavoring, high-fructose corn syrup, granulated sugar, fruit sugar, liquid sucrose, refined white sugar, and other food additive products. It also offers pasteurized milk, concentrated milk, powdered milk, cream, fermented milk, butter, cheese, and other dairy products; and fruit and vegetable juices, puree, fresh fruits and vegetables, canned foods, frozen fruits and vegetables, powders, extracts, and other fruit and vegetable products, as well as imports fish eggs, sushi toppings, and other processed marine products from overseas. In addition, the company provides green, matcha green, oolong, black, rooibos, blended, cocoa, herb, and other tea products, as well as other beverages. Further, it offers wastewater treatment systems, smart ceiling fans, and nozzle type steam traps. O'will Corporation was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
